               <p>My pocket was picked, on Thursday, in <placeName id="t17920523-83-crimeloc479">Grace Church Street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17920523-83-crimeloc479" type="placeName" value="Grace Church Street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17920523-83-crimeloc479" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920523-83-off477 t17920523-83-crimeloc479"></join>, about eleven o'clock; I was informed of it; I turned round and saw my handkerchief in Ruff's hands, and followed him (I gave no alarm) and saw him give it to Scruton; I took them to a constable, and from thence to Guildhall; the constable has the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17920523-83-person824">
                  JOHN
