             sworn.</p>
               <p>I produce the handkerchief; I received it from this Gentleman, the prosecutor. (Prosecutor deposes to the handkerchief.)</p>
               <p>The prisoners in their defence said that Ruff had picked it up, and that too by accident; and the other (Scruton) said he was a sailor, and that seeing the boy Ruff pick up the handkerchief he cried out, halves.</p>
               <p>BOTH <rs id="t17920523-83-verdict480" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17920523-83-verdict480" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
